body:
hello. as many of u know i was doin a thing earlier where i had ppl do stuff and then post screenshots 2 get my credits but that didn't work out. which i totally coolio understand.

here is a good old fashioned giveaway. post ur skype name and ur favorite picture of a bee below and i will put all the names in a random picker thing and the winner will get my 3000 credits ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

if you win i will be contacting u via skype so we can coordinate credit transferring.
EDIT: btw, it's however many credits i have when i pick the winner. so if by then i have 5000 credits the prize will raise to that amount. just as a side note.


format:

Skype name: [name]

Pic of bee:
http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/32/Bee-apis.jpg (just an example, pick a different bee if u want)

I will pick the winner monday, 20th of april, so be sure to enter below soon!
